    pub avg_duration_ms: u64,
    pub test_commands_by_kind: HashMap<String, u64>, // \"cargo test\", \"cargo nextest\", etc.
}
```

### 2. Track test-specific telemetry
```rust
// In execute_remote_compilation
if matches!(kind, Some(CompilationKind::CargoTest)) {
