The existing test suite in hook.rs has unit tests for classification but
lacks integration tests verifying end-to-end cargo test execution.

## Problem

Without integration tests:
1. Can't verify cargo test actually works end-to-end
2. Can't catch regressions in test execution
3. Can't verify output streaming, exit codes, etc.

## Proposed Solution

### 1. Add mock-based integration tests in hook.rs
```rust
#[tokio::test]
async fn test_cargo_test_remote_success() {
    // Setup mock daemon returning worker
    // Setup mock SSH to run command and return test output
    // Verify:
    // - Classification is CargoTest
    // - Worker selected
    // - Command executed
    // - Output streamed
    // - Exit 0 -> Deny (success)
}

#[tokio::test]
async fn test_cargo_test_remote_failures() {
    // Mock SSH returns exit 101 (test failures)
    // Verify:
    // - Output streamed
    // - Exit 101 -> Deny (test ran but failed)
}

#[tokio::test]
async fn test_cargo_test_build_failure() {
    // Mock SSH returns exit 1 (build error)
    // Verify:
    // - Error output streamed
    // - Exit 1 -> Deny
}
```

### 2. Add test output verification
```rust
#[tokio::test]
async fn test_cargo_test_output_streaming() {
    // Configure mock to return test output line by line
    // Verify all lines received in order
    // Verify colors preserved (if applicable)
}
```

### 3. Add E2E test script
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# scripts/test_cargo_test_e2e.sh
# With real workers (if available) or mock

# Test basic cargo test
echo \"Testing: cargo test\"
rch hook test --input '{\"tool\":\"Bash\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"cargo test\"}}' --verbose

# Test cargo test with filter
echo \"Testing: cargo test specific_test\"
rch hook test --input '{\"tool\":\"Bash\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"cargo test test_classify\"}}' --verbose
```

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Integration tests for cargo test success case
- [ ] Integration tests for test failure (exit 101)
- [ ] Integration tests for build failure (exit 1)
- [ ] Output streaming tests
- [ ] E2E test script for manual verification

